      *                                                                                       LUC109
      * If LUC109 is active, recalculate the Maximum End Date of Risk on the                  LUC109
      * Unicredito extension file based on the new Facility Expiry Date.                      LUC109
      *                                                                                       LUC109
     C           LUC109    IFEQ 'Y'                                                           LUC109
      *                                                                                       LUC109
     C           KFACH     CHAINFCLTYFX0             81                                       LUC109
     C           *IN81     IFEQ *OFF                                                          LUC109
      *                                                                                       LUC109
      * If the Type of Facility field is set to 'C', then the Maximum                         LUC109
      * End Date of Risk will be calculated as Facility Expiry Date + a                       LUC109
      * number of days. The number of days is found from the Maximum                          LUC109
      * Tenor field. If Max. Tenor is in the form 'nnM', then days =                          LUC109
      * nn x 31. If in the form 'nnY', then days = nn x 366.                                  LUC109
      *                                                                                       LUC109
     C                     MOVELLMAXT     WRK02   2                                           LUC109
     C                     MOVE WRK02     WMAX12  20                                          LUC109
     C                     MOVE LMAXT     WMAX3   1                                           LUC109
      *                                                                                       LUC109
     C           LFACT     IFEQ 'C'                                                           LUC109
     C           WMAX3     IFEQ 'M'                                                           LUC109
     C           WMAX12    MULT 31        LMEDR                                               LUC109
     C                     ADD  DTEX      LMEDR                                               LUC109
     C                     ENDIF                                                              LUC109
     C           WMAX3     IFEQ 'Y'                                                           LUC109
     C           WMAX12    MULT 366       LMEDR                                               LUC109
     C                     ADD  DTEX      LMEDR                                               LUC109
     C                     ENDIF                                                              LUC109
     C                     ENDIF                                                              LUC109
      *                                                                                       LUC109
     C           LFACT     IFEQ 'T'                                                           LUC109
     C                     Z-ADDDTEX      LMEDR                                               LUC109
     C                     ENDIF                                                              LUC109
      *                                                                                       LUC109
     C                     UPDATFCLTYFX0                                                      LUC109
      *                                                                                       LUC109
     C                     ENDIF                                                              LUC109
     C                     ENDIF                                                              LUC109
      *****************************************************************                       LUC109
      ** End of hook LEH00434                                                                 LUC109
      *****************************************************************                       LUC109
